title: Didn't recieve my mystery gift from riot.
body:
Hi Rioters, 

On this account I did not receive my mystery skin from Ocean week although I contributed 44 points or so.
I however have received the icon.

replies.body:
Hey Molozon,

They are distributing the gift in waves and are still in the process of doing so. Check this post for more details and updates; http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/announcements/LryNggNH-ocean-week-mystery-champion-update

-DTN
